content:
Monitors file changes for potential sensitive data like API keys, passwords, or personal information. Provides immediate alerts to prevent accidental commits of secrets.

```json
{
  "Notification": [
    {
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "if [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_NAME\" == 'Write' ]] || [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_NAME\" == 'Edit' ]]; then if grep -E '(api[_-]?key|secret|password|token|private[_-]?key)\\s*[:=]\\s*[\"\'][^\"\']+[\"\']' \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" 2>/dev/null | grep -v '\\*\\*\\*\\|example\\|placeholder\\|your[_-]'; then echo 'üö® SECURITY ALERT: Potential exposed secret in '$(basename \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\")' - Review immediately!'; fi; if grep -E '[A-Za-z0-9._%+-]+@[A-Za-z0-9.-]+\\.[A-Z|a-z]{2,}' \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" 2>/dev/null | head -1; then echo '‚ö†Ô∏è Email address detected - ensure this is intentional'; fi; fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
